### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:7071/api/CreateTask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "新しい請求書の作成",
  "priority": "High",
  "tags": ["Project", "CS"]
}
### Update an existing task
# IMPORTANT: Replace the ID below with the actual ID you copied from your browser!
PUT http://localhost:7071/api/UpdateTask/728628ac-b70a-4647-8555-a5df976b73e8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Inprogress",
  "title": "【更新済み】新しい請求書の作成"
}
### Delete a task
# IMPORTANT: Replace the ID below with the actual ID of the task!
DELETE http://localhost:7071/api/DeleteTask/728628ac-b70a-4647-8555-a5df976b73e8
